The paper discusses the optimization of deep linear residual networks, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the importance of initialization and optimization in deep linear neural networks, which could fall under cs.SI (Systems and Control) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
